| `20:16:37` | `api_action_check.headers/body` | `200`; decoded `{"consumed":true,"fetched":true}` | The backend recorded the old ray/token state as fetched and consumed after the premature `/p/` request. |
| `20:18:39` / `20:18:40` | `fresh_api_dl` / `fresh_api_cb` | both `200`; `dl` decoded `{"ok":true,"redir":""}`, `cb` body `1` | A fresh browser registration and click callback were accepted. |
